Glossary of terms used in this application

Site - an installation of the application on a particular website

Master Administrator - (Site Adminstrator/Owner) The person with access who oversees the site and should have complete control over it.

Backup Administrator - A user who has some rights to run some central functions on the site without being the owner.

Group - A set of users who have general visibility to each others wish lists. A user can be in multiple groups

Group Administrator - A user who runs administrative functions for a group.

Clan - ?

user - Any person who can log on to the site and/or who is represented in the wishlists and/or Secret Santa groups

Secret Santa Group - a set of users who draw each others names from a virtual hat for a gift exchange


